462
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:28,060
Pri tom malo verovatnom scenariju,

463
00:30:29,220 --> 00:30:31,480
ako ne možemo da se složimo,

464
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,850
onda, da.
Mislim, ne.

465
00:30:35,190 --> 00:30:36,860
U pravu ste.

466
00:30:37,610 --> 00:30:38,610
Ne trkate se.

