Otvori.
-Zaglavila su se.

1378
01:26:36,510 --> 01:26:37,380
Spremni?

1379
01:26:37,430 --> 01:26:38,840
Ime na sredini tog volana

1380
01:26:38,890 --> 01:26:41,510
govori da sam rođen
spreman, Šelbi. Nagazi.

1381
01:26:41,550 --> 01:26:43,100
Tako treba.

1382
01:26:46,020 --> 01:26:48,480
Malo trza, zar ne?

1383
01:26:48,900 --> 01:26:50,020
Otvori vrata.

1384
